Christina McHale of U.S. Upsets No. 8 Marion Bartoli at U.S. Open Tennis

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-08-31T20:02:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/christina-mchale-of-u-s-upsets-no-8-marion-bartoli-at-u-s-open-tennis.html
Christina McHale, a 19-year-old from
Englewood Cliffs,  New Jersey , upset No. 8 Marion Bartoli of
France 7-6 (7-2), 6-2 to reach the third round at the U.S. Open.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  